   ── Third-party notice ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   This peer links libsodium (ISC license, permissive and Apache-2.0-compatible)
   for Ed25519 + SHA-256. libsodium is the one runtime dependency; it is linked
   via pkg-config (the shared `.so` carries a normal `libsodium.so` runtime
   dependency; a fully-static consumer links libsodium statically). No libsodium
   source is redistributed here; see https://doc.libsodium.org/ for its license
   text.
